  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Continuous Action and Varied Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this top-down shooter, destroy enemies that attack in waves, each with different patterns and abilities, requiring you to quickly adapt your tactics. Use a variety of weapons to survive the most challenging confrontations and keep the action at a constant high pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong><br>Eliminate enemies to earn money for new weapons and upgrades. Choose your weapons strategically to create powerful combinations, adapting your playstyle each round. The more enemies you defeat, the more resources you'll have to strengthen your arsenal and survive the most brutal waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode and Score Challenge</strong><br>Face endless waves in an infinite mode where the difficulty keeps increasing. Survive as long as possible, test your reflexes and strategies, and compete for the highest score. Who will be the ultimate survivor?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to face the greatest threat of the future. Are you ready for battle?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/b8e02079a1fc1e6587eb46a8468519fb.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Continuous Action and Varied Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this top-down shooter, destroy enemies that attack in waves, each with different patterns and abilities, requiring you to quickly adapt your tactics. Use a variety of weapons to survive the most challenging confrontations and keep the action at a constant high pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/820eec30b79ef6c75f1e576f4cbb4080.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong><br>Eliminate enemies to earn money for new weapons and upgrades. Choose your weapons strategically to create powerful combinations, adapting your playstyle each round. The more enemies you defeat, the more resources you'll have to strengthen your arsenal and survive the most brutal waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.poster.avif?t=1769031213\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.webm?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441350/extras/44d82b128cdf5f91ad33c95f24c1427f.mp4?t=1769031213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode and Score Challenge</strong><br>Face endless waves in an infinite mode where the difficulty keeps increasing. Survive as long as possible, test your reflexes and strategies, and compete for the highest score. Who will be the ultimate survivor?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to face the greatest threat of the future. Are you ready for battle?</p>",
